name: AbstractGroup
text:
Abstract base class for all kinds of groups. AbstractGroup
is not generally useful to instantiate on its own.

attrs.name: callback
descs: A callback to run in the browser whenever a button group is manipulated.

attrs.name: labels
descs: List of text labels contained in this group.
